dataList.content: The atmosphere here seems rather different. It appears that a different Syndicate controls the second floor.

dataList.title: Los Mariachis
dataList.content: Hey, oigan! What’s with all the doom and gloom on your faces?

dataList.title: Los Mariachis
dataList.content: Don’t you know the floor rules? Sour looks are a no-no, so put a hat over your long face!
Are you talking to me? Keep staring and I'll S.Y.N.C., that what you want?
<Come on, Ryōshū… Can we please stop immediately resorting to violence—>

dataList.title: Los Mariachis
dataList.content: Ey, never mind that. This one's mug is even nastier, no? Which hand's supposed to be your eyes?
